nanosite is the tiny huge static site generator. 

# tiny
Minimalism is empowering. nanosite was created as a response to traditional site generators that force your content to conform to 
nanosite imposes no restriction on the structure of your site. So you can finally control every detail of your site's design, whether you're making a blog, organization page or portfolio.

# huge
nanosite is packed with useful features.

- Powerful templating language
- Built-in server &mdash; develop your site live
- Markdown, RSS
